From whatever available resources the masjid had they utilize the area to the best extends. Secondly this place is located in the most commercial hub of the city. In my view most convenient transportation to this place is 2 wheeler vehicles. Vijayawada railway station is quite nearby.

Good about the masjid is they are providing Islamic education to khawateen (Female). Definitely it was good move by the masjid responsible people. Such programs are needed in all the masjids of vijayawada. Those who gain Islamic elm from such places, we pray they spread tawheed with in their house and then rest palace's (ameen).

featured_reviews.review_id:
Mashallah!!! A very good function hall(shadi khana) at a very low price all over in the whole city. One with a very good idea can make the function in a very good manner by utilising the entire Eadgah.
First of all, this is an Islamic Function hall and this is permissible only for Muslim Functions.

The best thing is, this Moti Masjid provides function hall in a very low rentals for the people who are in the same area.

As most of the reviewers said , on the Islamic Holy festivals like Eid-ul-Fitr and Eid-ul-Adha
prayer(namaz) is offered in the eadgah which is worth a blessing to offer and watch. Mashallah!!

Function hall can be maintained more neatly by the committee like cleaning the hall, fans, roofs, pillars etc.. if this is done, this function hall would be the best in the city.
